Package: seafisheries
Title: Clustering Tools for Fisheries Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Romain", "Forestier", , "romainf@spc.int", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions and tutorials for processing and clustering fisheries 
    operational data for use with SEAPODYM models. Includes coordinate conversion,
    data cleaning, and spatial filtering utilities.
